data.description: Welcome to Solara Lofts! This units comes fully furnished and ready to move in! These luxury lofts feature granite counters, European cabinetry, custom built bookcase and large, oversized windows. conveniently located just minutes away from SD Airport, Little Italy, Balboa Park, The Embarcadero and Gaslamp District- You will love the lifestyle of this 3rd floor, open concept! Bathroom offers full tub/ shower. Many extra's such as, full size newer washer & brand new dryer in unit, stainless steel appliances, gorgeous flooring, two parking spaces and A/C.  Solara Lofts amenities are a plus, which include, secured entry door access, secure private underground parking garage, beautiful lobby for you or your guests to meet and lounge in on your way to city fun, a spa, racquetball, gym, massage room, and night security. Enjoy the nightlife and catch a big league game, concert or other special event just minutes away! So whether a student steps away at the nearby law college, a professional, seasonal tourist looking for a great landing spot for when your in town for such a great price this one will not last!
